{
  "info": {
    "name": "RBAC Multi-Model System",
    "description": "Enterprise RBAC — pre-filled with real seeded DB values.\n\n**Key facts (from testing session):**\n- All endpoints require Bearer auth except POST /auth/login and POST /auth/refresh\n- Login body must include tenantId\n- JWT claims keep JWT names (sub, tid, tv) — no ClaimTypes remapping\n- PolicyEffect: 1=Allow, 2=Deny (integer in JSON)\n- ConditionTreeJson: serialised JSON string\n- Delegator (delegator@acme.test) has content-editor role in ALPHA scope only — delegation uses scopeId_alpha\n- Audit log from/to must be UTC ISO-8601 (e.g. 2026-01-01T00:00:00Z)\n- Super-admin bypasses tenant isolation middleware\n\n**Run order:** Login → Refresh → Roles → Policies → Delegations → Permission Checks → Audit Logs",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },

